<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hello all,<p>

I have a quick question conserning illusions.  I'm a 17 lv high elf chanter.  I have been soloing using charm after picking up charm at 12th.  I think it is the best spell we have as enchanters.  <p>

My question is this.  I tend to hunt camps, so I tend to be there for many hours at a time.  Well at night, I like to change to a dark elf for the ultravision.  I have not been able to find the hide ability though.  Is it possible that only certain abilities are gained during an illusion?  It would be nice to be able to break the charm with hiding.  Any thoughts and help would be appreciated.<p>

Jujucharm</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
